# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/media-libs/mesa/ChangeLog,v 1.646 2015/07/02 01:10:56 mattst88 Exp $

  02 Jul 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> -mesa-10.5.4.ebuild,
  -mesa-10.5.5.ebuild, -mesa-10.5.6.ebuild:
  Drop old.

*mesa-10.6.1 (02 Jul 2015)

  02 Jul 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.6.1.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.6.1.

*mesa-10.5.8 (02 Jul 2015)

  02 Jul 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.8.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.8.

  13 Jun 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Apply patch for bug #543566 to mesa-10.3.7-r1 too.

*mesa-10.5.6 (24 May 2015)

  24 May 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.6.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.6.

  24 May 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.2.8.ebuild,
  mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild, mesa-10.3.7-r2.ebuild, mesa-10.4.6.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Drop r600-llvm-compiler USE flag.

  11 May 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> -mesa-10.4.4.ebuild,
  -mesa-10.5.1.ebuild, -mesa-10.5.2.ebuild:
  Drop old.

*mesa-10.5.5 (11 May 2015)

  11 May 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.5.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.5.

*mesa-10.4.6 (28 Apr 2015)

  28 Apr 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.4.6.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.4.6.

*mesa-10.5.4 (27 Apr 2015)

  27 Apr 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.4.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.4, bug #547686.

  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> mesa-10.2.8.ebuild,
  mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild, mesa-10.3.7-r2.ebuild, mesa-10.4.4.ebuild,
  mesa-10.5.1.ebuild, mesa-10.5.2.ebuild:
  Drop old Python implementations

  31 Mar 2015; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> mesa-7.10.3.ebuild,
  mesa-10.2.8.ebuild, mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild, mesa-10.3.7-r2.ebuild,
  mesa-10.4.4.ebuild, mesa-10.5.1.ebuild, mesa-10.5.2.ebuild:
  Update dependency after package move of eselect modules to app-eselect.

  30 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.5.2.ebuild:
  Move python deps back, bug 545058.

*mesa-10.5.2 (28 Mar 2015)

  28 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.2.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.2. Fixes bugs 542808 and 542812.

  24 Mar 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  mesa-10.5.1.ebuild:
  Apply patch to fix build problem, bug #543566.

  24 Mar 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  +files/mesa-10.5.1-fstat-include.patch, mesa-10.5.1.ebuild:
  Apply patch to fix build problem, bug #543566.

  17 Mar 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  mesa-10.2.8.ebuild, mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild, mesa-10.3.7-r2.ebuild,
  mesa-10.4.4.ebuild, mesa-10.5.1.ebuild:
  Adjust dependencies on llvm versions to match working combinations. Restore
  keywords that appear to have been mistakenly dropped.

  14 Mar 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #530652

  14 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop dead USE flags.

  14 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> -mesa-7.11.2.ebuild,
  -mesa-8.0.4-r1.ebuild, -mesa-9.0.3.ebuild, -mesa-9.1.6.ebuild,
  -mesa-9.2.5-r1.ebuild, -mesa-10.0.4.ebuild, -mesa-10.1.6.ebuild,
  -mesa-10.4.3.ebuild, -files/mesa-8.0-dont-require-llvm-for-r300.patch,
  -files/mesa-8.0.4-configure-bsd.patch,
  -files/mesa-8.1-dont-require-llvm-for-r300.patch,
  -files/mesa-9.2-dont-require-llvm-for-r300.patch,
  -files/eselect-mesa.conf.7.11, -files/eselect-mesa.conf.8.0.1,
  -files/eselect-mesa.conf.8.1:
  Drop old.

*mesa-10.5.1 (14 Mar 2015)

  14 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.1.ebuild,
  -mesa-10.5.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.1.

  06 Mar 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #530652).

  03 Mar 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> mesa-10.4.4.ebuild:
  add arm64 support, tested on A53 board

  01 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> -mesa-10.3.5.ebuild:
  Drop old.

  01 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org>
  +files/mesa-10.3.7-format_utils.c.patch, mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild,
  mesa-10.3.7-r2.ebuild:
  Add patch to reduce compile time/memory, bug 540960.

  01 Mar 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.5.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Drop r600-llvm-compiler USE flag. Upstream only wants active developers to use
  this.

  28 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.0.4.ebuild,
  mesa-10.1.6.ebuild, mesa-10.2.8.ebuild, mesa-10.3.5.ebuild,
  mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild, mesa-10.3.7-r2.ebuild, mesa-10.4.3.ebuild,
  mesa-10.4.4.ebuild, mesa-10.5.0_rc3.ebuild, mesa-7.10.3.ebuild,
  mesa-7.11.2.ebuild, mesa-8.0.4-r1.ebuild, mesa-9.0.3.ebuild,
  mesa-9.1.6.ebuild, mesa-9.2.5-r1.ebuild:
  Add bindist restriction, bug 541494.

  28 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> -mesa-10.5.0_rc1.ebuild:
  Drop old.

*mesa-10.5.0_rc3 (28 Feb 2015)

  28 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.0_rc3.

  24 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #530652

  23 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #530652

  22 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.5.0_rc1.ebuild:
  Add missing PYTHON_USEDEP to mako dependency, bug 540968.

  22 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #530652

  21 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.0.4.ebuild,
  mesa-10.2.8.ebuild:
  Require llvm for opencl, bug 516790.

  21 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.0.4.ebuild:
  Bump llvm requirement from 3.2 to 3.3, bug 506180.

  21 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #530652

*mesa-10.5.0_rc1 (21 Feb 2015)

  21 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-10.5.0_rc1.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.5.0_rc1.

  20 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #530652

  19 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #530652

  18 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #530652

  16 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mesa-10.2.8.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #513736

  10 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.4.4.ebuild:
  Remove opencl-libdir once again.

  10 Feb 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  mesa-10.4.4.ebuild:
  Remove build fix again as it was already applied upstream, bug #539626.

  10 Feb 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  mesa-10.4.4.ebuild:
  Re-apply build and dependency fixes which were mistakenly dropped, bug
  #538086.

*mesa-10.3.7-r1 (08 Feb 2015)
*mesa-10.3.7-r2 (08 Feb 2015)

  08 Feb 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  +mesa-10.3.7-r1.ebuild, +mesa-10.3.7-r2.ebuild, -mesa-10.3.7.ebuild:
  Add ebuild which works with old eselect-opengl for stabilization in bug
  #530652.

*mesa-10.4.4 (08 Feb 2015)

  08 Feb 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  +mesa-10.4.4.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Version bump. Add d3d9 flag, bug #537494.

  04 Feb 2015; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> mesa-10.2.8.ebuild:
  ia64 stable, bug #513736 by Émeric Maschino

  03 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> -mesa-10.3.5-r1.ebuild,
  -mesa-10.4.2.ebuild:
  Remove old.

*mesa-10.4.3 (03 Feb 2015)

  03 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org>
  +files/mesa-10.3.7-dont-use-clrsb.patch, +mesa-10.4.3.ebuild,
  mesa-10.3.7.ebuild:
  Version bump to 10.4.3. Fix bugs 536916 and 538086.

  13 Jan 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.4.2.ebuild:
  Drop usage of --with-opencl-libdir, bug 536458.

  13 Jan 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> mesa-10.4.2.ebuild:
  Require libelf for USE=opencl, bug 536456.

*mesa-10.3.7 (12 Jan 2015)
