*mesa-8.0 (10 Feb 2012)

  10 Feb 2012; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +mesa-8.0.ebuild,
  +files/mesa-8.0-dont-require-llvm-for-r300.patch,
  +files/eselect-mesa.conf.8.0, metadata.xml:
